    "date": "2021-07-13T18:28:59Z",
    "text": "Emergency Housing Voucher Act of 2021\n\nThis bill provides additional FY2021 funding for emergency rental assistance vouchers through the Department of Housing and Urban Development for families and individuals who are (1) experiencing homelessness; (2) at risk of homelessness; (3) fleeing, or attempting to flee, domestic violence and other dangerous situations; or (4) recently homeless."
